This time last year I was limping, asking my friends to walk slower, freaking myself out by reading webMD, and crying in my kitchen thinking I would never walk right again, never chase kids, never run a race, never not feel the constant pain in my foot. 

I feel really proud of the routine and PT with @mpgonewellness that has led me to be able to do the show without feeling like I needed to stand on one foot the whole time. 

I am finally wearing real shoes again and I had forgotten how much fun it is. I discovered @baredfootwear for press events and Iâ€™m never going back.

#PlasticFreeJuly has officially begun.

Weâ€™re proud to join the global movement tackling plastic pollution this Plastic Free July. At Bared, we envision a future for footwear that's free from plastic.
Sourcing 100% plastic-free materials for footwear is a difficult task. 

Unlike standard apparel, shoes endure constant impact, requiring highly durable materials. Plastic has been the go-to material in footwear for far too long.

You may not realise that 70% of the outsoles marketed as "rubber" are synthetic. Even where natural rubber is used in outsoles, it typically must be strengthened with petrochemical-based curatives.

In 2023, we proudly began the rollout of PLIANTâ„¢ outsoles across our womenâ€™s range. Developed by the innovators at @@nfw_tech , PLIANTâ„¢ soles are the worldâ€™s first naturally cured performance outsoles.

100% Plastic-Free. 100% Returns to Earth.

Our partnership with NFW and the launch of PLIANT mark significant milestones in our plastic-free journey at Bared. And weâ€™re just getting started. 

#baredfootwear #plantsnotplastic

Who's participating in FEBFAST?
To support all the wonderful people participating in FEBFAST this month we are dedicating February to inspire good habits and promote general health and wellbeing.

During this time we will be hosting a giveaway, posting inspirational content, as well as teaming up with a few more health brands.

Lets kick start a healthy year and reconnect with our ying and our yang!  #febfast #heathyhabits #baredhealthrevolution

We thought we'd kick start our healthy FEBFAST feed with this smoothie recipe from @thehealthyingredient considering the crazy heat that has taken over Melbourne. 
If you are participating in FebFast Australia we would love to hear what habit you are kicking this month to support a great cause:) The Healthy Ingredient Blueberry, Banana and Chia Smoothie.

1 banana
1 cup frozen blueberries
2TBS Five:am organic yoghurt (vanilla bean)
1TBS chia seeds
1/4 avocado
Preferred milk
Blend and serve! Serves 1 for breakfast or 2 as a snack.

If you loved this smoothie recipe check out The Healthy Ingredients website http://www.thehealthyingredient.com.au
